            <description><![CDATA[<pre>Fixes\n- Cloud Transcription now keeps each transcript segment as its own block instead of merging adjacent segments from the same speaker.\n- Speaker names remain clickable per segment for quick rename/edit flows.\n\nBackend\n- New recordings now use transcript segments when deciding whether to auto-generate a summary, so provider-generated short overview text no longer causes long recordings to skip summary generation.</pre>]]></description>
